                                                                                            </div>
                                                                                <div class="text-wrap">
                                            <h1><strong><i>NEW!  </i></strong>Thomson Glide Screw™</h1>
                                            <p>
        <p>Part linear bearing, part lead screw, the Glide Screw™ from Thomson combines the best features of these products into an easy to install, one-part solution. </p>
        <p>In addition, the Glide Screw eliminates alignment issues and comes standard with Thomson’s patented Lube-for-Life technology for zero maintenance. Additional high heat, vacuum/cleanroom, and food grade configurations are available.  If you don’t see a standard model that meets your needs, contact Thomson - we do custom configurations upon request.</p>
    </p>
                                        </div>
